{"tid":2131553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【7月30日今晚香港時間9點】日本版人權法終於有眉目！！一齊加速推到上trend","createTime":"2020-07-30T02:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T02:02:32.000Z","uid":74888,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"234624c18cde249169c23c72aa992c95c9128798","tid":2131553,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"purple\"><strong>突發！日本戰線全民感謝祭 </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔同國家都陸陸續續因為支那監生通過國安法而開始有所動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係各位香港人屌緊無限咁多野，國安又開始行動既同時, 日本既手足成功推動國會議員去支持訂立人權法!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fYDJpsY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfYDJpsY.jpg&h=dd32125f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>佢地分別係：（以下全部都係議員） 山尾志桜里 中谷元 長島昭久 有村治子 藤末健三 山田宏 桜井周 井上一徳 串田誠一 </em> &larr;唔該同我認住佢地！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，有一班日本議員組成左<span class=\"blue\">JPAC(Japan Parliamentary Alliance on China, 對中政策國會議員聯盟)</span> <br />\n而喺發佈會上，JPAC公佈左日本版嘅人權法案嘅建議案嘅同時，佢地同時建議咗一個針對香港人嘅救生艇計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>計劃內容 </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"maroon\">1. 人權法</span></strong><br />\n- 條例並非只對應香港，而是對違反國際人權法者，而日本唔可以坐視不理嘅為所進行的制裁行動<br />\n- 對有違人權法人士進行凍結資產<br />\n- 拒絶有違人權法人士入國或遞解出境<br />\n- 對受害者進行支援行動<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">簡單啲黎講即係班仆街以後冇撚得黎日本而且手足可以得到支援！！</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"maroon\">2. 救生艇計劃</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n- 自民黨中谷元表示，<span class=\"red\">成員將跨黨派合作，協助港人以及制止北京違反人權。</span><br />\n- 組織亦計劃<span class=\"red\">要求政府放寬港人留日工作簽證申請條件</span>，以及延長港人免簽證留日期限。<br />\n- 山尾志桜里亦表示，<span class=\"red\">如有國安法相關的案件要求日本引渡香港人，希望日本政府可以清楚拒絕</span>。她表示，未必一定能全面取消引渡協議，但會完善搜查程序，盡力保護香港人。<br />\n<br />\n詳細記招報導內容請參考立場新聞&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30ZKZnc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30ZKZnc&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=8ea9e214\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30ZKZnc</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"purple\">We need your help!!! </span></strong></span><br />\n我地在日既香港人係到呼籲各位連登仔今晚香港時間9點一齊推<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">#対中政策に関する国会議員連盟 <br />\n#JPAC <br />\n#ThankYouJapan</span><br />\n呢3個hashtag上twitter trend等日本既議員都知道香港人有留意佢地，令更多議員支持人權法，加速法案通過生效！！<br />\n人地冒住犯國安法第38條幫緊我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTweet既內容交比各位連登仔自由發fight!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得加 <br />\n<span class=\"blue\">#対中政策に関する国会議員連盟 <br />\n#JPAC <br />\n#ThankYouJapan</span><br />\n<br />\n又或者用我地既日文TEMPLATE<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"violet\">日本国会議員の皆さん、香港を応援していただきありがとうございます。どうか力をお貸しください<br />\n</span><br />\n<span class=\"blue\">#対中政策に関する国会議員連盟 #JPAC #ThankYouJapan</span><br />\n<em><span class=\"small\">中文翻譯：<br />\n各位日本國會議員，感謝你地支持香港。請拍爛檔幫幫我地</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>內容點都好記得加hashtag!! (好重要所以要講3次!!!)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n廢話講完各位連登仔開波做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有麻煩各位唔該記住呢班議員（我地既大恩人）既名！！"},{"pid":"3c17cc17ac8b03a8c4a997e8f66553078c2bd5ca","tid":2131553,"uid":361247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T02:58:22.000Z","msg":"期待日本出手救香港人"},{"pid":"3d5f4b91fa184cee2773c2ed39eba2a0d1d797e7","tid":2131553,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T02:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa63cd2d52c037c3fbacc0cd1e551d53ba089250","tid":2131553,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T02:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47a750930683a9ec571b60fcdb0653afbf89b40","tid":2131553,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb49bc8ec06a89924d99c8e6cc0f9251fca53ef","tid":2131553,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:01:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dba765ec0ccc21e82c69cf85087b68d7d52c1bee","tid":2131553,"uid":62305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efe87d24c72243d02397e0e47c8330f4f89a12f","tid":2131553,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867a4efb3cbc347c39d366e7aaf501bfd6a84f8a","tid":2131553,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T0